header.name: Secret Halls of the Fallen Emperor
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: For many years the halls of the Fallen Emperor were considered lost. Lately they were squatted by a gang of bandits. The halls of the Fallen Emperor are home to a highly valued specie of fungi.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A medium trunk containing a chainmail.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A sign on the floor: THE FALLEN EMPEROR LIVES

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: A huge gate with two keyholes on the eastern wall.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A chest with an iron key in it.

game_elements.name: Item 5
game_elements.description: An iron key tucked under some debris.

game_elements.name: Item 6
game_elements.description: Remains of a wizard apparently killed by humans, a strange, made of an unknown material katana clutched in his hands.

game_elements.name: Item 7
game_elements.description: An uncanny, covered with hieroglyphs object in a glass curio case.

game_elements.name: Item 8
game_elements.description: An ornate lantern, swears when lit.
